title: Cryptographically signed audit trail
---
Add HMAC-SHA256 signatures to audit log entries for tamper detection and non-repudiation. Audit is currently append-only but unsigned. Reuses existing HMAC chain infrastructure already proven in AuditChain.v (F3). Formalize signature chain in AuditSigning.v (F13) and extract. Core placement.